hermore, each TCEHK withdrawal is manually audited by at least two TCEHK employees before being sent. There are no private keys on any cloud server and all funds are stored using deep cold storage.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">All deposit addresses sent by the TCEHK system are verified by a third-party server to ensure they contain keys controlled by the founder. If the public keys do not match, the system will shut down immediately, stopping all transactions.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><br/></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">system security</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: 