er-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">8. User verification</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">8.1. All transactions require identification and verification procedures (&quot;Know Your Customer&quot; or &quot;KYC&quot;). All existing users and new users of the platform must pass a verification procedure. TCEHK reserves the right to restrict the platform functions of users who have not passed the verification program. If the user refuses to provide the documents and information required by KYC, TCEHK reserves the right to immediately terminate the provision of services to the user.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">8.2. The user promises to provide TCEHK with relevant documents containing correct personal information. If the user provides forged documents and false personal information, TCEHK can suspend, cancel or terminate the user&#39;s account and freeze the funds it deems appropriate.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">8.3. The user hereby authorizes TCEHK to directly or indirectly (through a third party) conduct any inquiry it deems necessary to verify the relevance and accuracy of the information provided for verification purposes. The scope of the personal data to be transferred will be limited to the necessary evidence, and security measures will be taken to protect the data.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">8.4. The user hereby agrees to abide by the effective anti-money laundering (AML) policy and Know Your Customer (KYC) policy issued by TCEHK from time to time.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">9. Account maintenance</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">9.1. This platform is only for users&#39; personal and non-commercial use. TCEHK is always vigilant in maintaining the security of the platform and services. By accessing the platform or using the service, the user agrees to provide TCEHK with current, accurate and complete personal information according to the prompts in the registration process, and is obliged to continuously update the relevant information.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">9.2. The user is only allowed to register one account on the platform. Therefore, any additional accounts may be suspended.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">9.3. The user agrees that it will not use any account other than the user&#39;s own account, nor will it access any other user&#39;s account at any time or assist others in obtaining unauthorized access or conducting any related transaction activities.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">9.4. TCEHK reserves the right to set an amount limit for account deposits/withdrawals/balances. TCEHK can also set daily, monthly and per transaction amount limits.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">9.5. The user is responsible for keeping the user account information confidential, including but not limited to the user&#39;s password, email, wallet address, wallet balance, and all activities including transactions conducted through his account. If there is any suspicious activity related to the user&#39;s account, TCEHK may ask the user to provide additional information, including verification documents, and may suspend the account and/or freeze the funds during the review period. The user hereby agrees to comply with the security requirements or accept the suspension and freezing.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">9.6. In any case where TCEHK&#39;s prior express permission is not obtained, the creation or use of accounts will cause all such accounts and user accounts as well as all pending buy/sell orders issued from these accounts to be immediately suspended. Any attempt to do so or assist others (users or other third parties) to do so, or any instructions, software or tools issued for this purpose will result in the termination of unauthorized accounts and user accounts. Termination is not the only remedy for such violations, and TCEHK may decide to take further action against users.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">10. Transaction</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">10.1. The platform allows users to submit orders to buy or sell cryptocurrency contracts.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">10.2. The user agrees that the order should only be submitted after careful consideration, and the user understands and accepts the consequences of its execution. The user agrees that once the order is executed, such transactions will be irreversible and cannot be cancelled.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">10.3. The user acknowledges and agrees that if the destination tag is not specified or displayed incorrectly (especially XRP) or the reference number is specified incorrectly (for TEDA currency transactions), the user may lose the deposit or the processing speed of the related request will be lower In order of priority.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">10.4. The minimum order amount is 10 TEDA and the maximum order amount is 20,000 TEDA. TCEHK reserves the right to change the minimum and maximum order amounts, and the relevant information will be displayed on the transaction page when the order is placed.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">10.5. The user acknowledges and agrees that due to certain over-the-counter transaction verification procedures and the inherent nature of the cryptocurrency network, the deposit and withdrawal transactions of TEDA coins may be delayed.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">10.6. If the user finds suspicious transactions or activities (including but not limited to unknown deposits and withdrawals) in the user account that are not initiated by the user, he should immediately notify TCEHK of the relevant facts and follow the instructions issued by TCEHK. Otherwise, TCEHK reserves the right to suspend the account and freeze the funds in it until the end of the investigation.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">10.7. TCEHK can cancel or recall any executed withdrawal transaction at the request of any financial institution (including but not limited to over-the-counter trading institutions). In this case, the user is obliged to cooperate with TCEHK to find out the reason for the request.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">10.8. The minimum deposit amount for TEDA coins is 200 TEDA coins. If the amount is less than the specified amount, the funds will not be credited to the user&#39;s account.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">11. Margin trading</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">11.1. Margin trading is applicable to long positions and short positions, depending on the specific fees, limits and conditions specified by TCEHK. ..</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">11.2. TCEHK may charge fees for opening and/or closing positions and overnight fees.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">11.3. The user acknowledges and agrees that, in order to prevent the account balance from becoming a negative number, when the price of any underlying cryptocurrency reaches the &quot;stop loss price&quot; value specified when the user opens a position, TCEHK has the right to close any position regardless of whether the user is notified.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">11.4. The user acknowledges and agrees that, in order to lock in its profits, when the price of the underlying cryptocurrency is close to the &quot;Take Profit Price&quot; value specified when the user opens a position, TCEHK has the right to close any position regardless of whether the user is notified or not. The user further acknowledges and agrees that the highest take-profit price (&quot;Maximum Take-Profit Price&quot;) set by any user when opening any position will be subject to the maximum take-profit price limit set by TCEHK from time to time.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">11.5. If the user does not have sufficient funds to pay the relevant fees, TCEHK reserves the right to close any of its positions without prior notice to the user.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">11.6. The user acknowledges and agrees that due to including but not limited to the instant changes in the cryptocurrency contract market and the discontinuity of the K-line chart, the closing price displayed on the platform when the user is about to close the position may be slightly different from the actual closing price of the user. .</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">12. Overnight fee</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">12.1. If the user does not choose to open the &quot;hold position overnight&quot; option, any cryptocurrency contract will be closed at 6 a.m. Singapore time (UTC +8) (the &quot;closing time&quot;).</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">12.2. If the user chooses to open the &quot;hold position overnight&quot; option, an overnight fee will be paid to TCEHK.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">12.3. The overnight fee will be charged daily at 30% of the commission when the user opens a position.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">12.4. The overnight fee will be directly deducted from the TEDA balance in the user&#39;s account. If the balance of TEDAcoin is lower than the overnight fee to be deducted, TCEHK will automatically deactivate the &quot;hold position overnight&quot; option, and the position will be closed at the closing time of the day. Any overnight fees charged from the user account are non-refundable.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">12.5. TCEHK reserves the right to change the amount and charging method of the overnight fee.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">13. Commission</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">13.1. The user agrees to pay a commission to TCEHK for each completed transaction.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">13.2. Before the transaction, the user must consider the commission rate announced by the platform on the website, application and the terms of use. However, TCEHK reserves the right to change the commission rate from time to time and will update the website, application and the terms of use accordingly.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">13.3. When the user opens a position, the commission amount will be automatically deducted from the deposit in the form of TEDA coins. The user is responsible for ensuring that the account has sufficient funds for margin trading and payment of commissions when opening a position. Unless the user has sufficient funds for margin trading and payment of commissions, cryptocurrency contract orders will not be executed.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">13.4. Commissions are charged based on each order (cryptocurrency contract) according to the following formula: commission = margin trading * (leverage multiple -1) * commission rate. For example, if the user chooses to open a long or short position with a commission rate of 0.15% by using 100 TEDA and 10 times leverage, the user needs to pay 3.6 TEDA (100 TEDA*(10-1)* 0.15%). TCEHK can decide to set and update the available leverage multiples and corresponding commission rates from time to time at its sole discretion.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">13.5. TCEHK may at its sole discretion change or review commissions, other fees and charging procedures from time to time, and such changes will take effect as soon as they are posted on the website and application.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">14. Rounding policy</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">14.1. For all financial calculations, TCEHK may use rounding policies that are beneficial to the platform. TCEHK rounds TEDA to the second digit after the separator. The rounding policy of other cryptocurrencies depends on different cryptocurrencies.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(99, 112, 133); font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">14.2. For the purpose of process optimization, transactions on certain currencies (including but not limited to TEDA and other cryptocurrencies) on the platform will not be reflected in user accounts, but as long as a unit as a whole meets the rounding standard, it will It is immediately displayed in the user account.</span></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; marg